A 1/5ths full bucket is used in Peer the Seer's trial for the quest The Fremennik Trials.

Changes[edit | edit source]

Date Changes
28 November –
18 December 2006

The "Drop" option was replaced with a "Destroy" option, so players could not cheat the puzzle by getting multiple containers.

22 March 2006
(update)

The item was graphically updated.

5 July –
19 September 2005

The item's examine was changed from "This bucket is twenty percent full. It has a 5 painted on it's[sic] side." to "This bucket is twenty percent full. It has a 5 painted on its side."
